OL,3,CDrivers stranded on side of A-road
OL,4,Cafter large pothole damages cars
OL,6,FDrivers were left stranded on the side
OL,7,Fof the A303 near Basingstoke after a
OL,8,Flarge pothole damaged dozens of
OL,9,Fvehicles.
OL,11,FMore than 30 cars had burst tyres and
OL,12,Fsome motorists had to wait for hours
OL,13,Fto be recovered.
OL,15,FPart of the slip road, which joins the
OL,16,FM3, has closed but those affected say
OL,17,Fthey're outraged that the road has
OL,18,Fbeen left in such poor condition.
