OL,3,CDrivers stranded on side of A-road
OL,4,Cafter large pothole damages cars
OL,6,FColin Harding hit the pothole and said
OL,7,Fit was "unavoidable" due to the high
OL,8,Flevels of traffic on the road.
OL,10,FColin said: "It caused major problems
OL,11,Ffor the other drivers there. I damaged
OL,12,Fmy car and had two burst tyres and I
OL,13,Fpotentially damaged both wheels as
OL,14,Fwell.
OL,16,F"It was frustrating for everybody.
OL,17,FThere were eight or nine other cars at
OL,18,Fthat point that had the same damage."
