OL,3,CDrivers stranded on side of A-road
OL,4,Cafter large pothole damages cars
OL,6,FNational Highways said the pothole had
OL,7,Fbeen repaired after it was initially
OL,8,Freported.
OL,10,FAn inspection was then carried out on
OL,11,FThursday but the agency said "adverse
OL,12,Fweather conditions" of Storm Goretti
OL,13,Fcaused the repair "to fail".
OL,15,FTraffic officers out on patrol went to
OL,16,Fhelp after coming across three
OL,17,Fvehicles on the hard shoulder of the
OL,18,FM3 just after 7pm on Thursday.
