OL,3,CDrivers stranded on side of A-road
OL,4,Cafter large pothole damages cars
OL,6,FNational Highways said their staff
OL,7,Fwere told the damage to vehicles was
OL,8,Fcaused by a pothole on the A303 entry
OL,9,Fslip road prior to joining the
OL,10,Fmotorway.
OL,12,FA maintenance team was then sent to
OL,13,Frepair the road.
OL,15,FThe inner lane of the slip road was
OL,16,Fclosed on Friday (9 January) for
OL,17,Fsafety reasons and whilst further
OL,18,Fassessments could be carried out.
