OL,3,CDrivers stranded on side of A-road
OL,4,Cafter large pothole damages cars
OL,6,FFurther repairs are due to take place
OL,7,Fon the slip road surface on Friday
OL,8,Fnight.
OL,10,FA National Highways spokesperson said:
OL,11,F"Safety is our primary concern, and we
OL,12,Fset stringent standards for pothole
OL,13,Frepairs on our roads.
OL,15,F"We regularly carry out inspections to
OL,16,Fhelp reduce the potential for potholes
OL,17,Fto form. We also encourage members of
OL,18,Fthe public to tell us if they find any
OL,19,Fpotholes so that we can repair them as
OL,20,Fswiftly as possible.
