OL,6,F"When potholes do occur, we repair
OL,7,Fthem as soon as possible, and any
OL,8,Fdefects that pose a risk to safety are
OL,9,Frepaired within 24 hours.
OL,11,F"People can report potholes to the
OL,12,FNational Highways Customer Contact
OL,13,FCentre by calling 0300 123 5000,
OL,14,Femail, on X or by visiting our
OL,15,Fwebsite."
